            Explore Mindvalley Programs →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-12 border-t border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Related Articles</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a href="/mindset-training/" class="bg-[#1A1A2E] rounded-xl p-6 border border-transparent hover:border-[#D4AF37]/40 transition-all"><h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Complete Mindset Training Guide</h3><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Everything you need to build a powerful success mindset.</p></a>
